Text:
I actually made an account because I couldn't resist commenting on this track. It has some background static to the beat and when compared to other torrents like this one: http://thepiratebay.se/torrent/7028295/Katy_Perry_-_Part_Of_Me__2012-Single__%5BNL%5D you can tell that it's lacking.

I suggest you don't waste your time, or download both and see for yourself.

@BaronVonWatermelon - If you listened to this at all you should immediately notice the muddy tones which strongly indicate that this is actually a lower bitrate version simply converted to 320kbps. His comment was actually pretty useful as it not only informed us of the sound problem but it provided link to a much cleaner version. (Criticism with solution is constructive.)
